description:
TPO 14/06 - T1 (Laurels) - reduce by 30% in height to max 3m from ground level;
T2 (Ash) - remove lower scaffold limbs to reduce the size of the canopy and crown lift to minimum 5m from ground level;
T3 - T7 (Ash) - crown reduce by 3m and crown lifted to minimum 6m from ground level;
T8 (Plum) and T9 (Apple - dead) - fell to 50mm from ground level;
T10 (Beech) - crown reduce by 2m and crown lift to minimum 6m from ground level;
Clear area of all self-seeded trees and scrub growth; and
T11 (Lime x 3) and T12 (London Plane) - crown reduce each tree by 3m and crown lift to minimum 6m from ground level. (Summary).
